{"tid":1429192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊位街坊琴晚係深水埗警署外有份幫個入唔到去報到嘅叔叔，可以入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:42.000Z","uid":250594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65d054de0ce527a1f18cd3a6860da4612177e3c6","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"非鬼p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你行開左之後叔叔都keep住好不安想走<br />\n我又攔唔住佢所以離開左安全島，所以你可能搵唔番我地<br />\n不過我有一直跟到叔叔去佢架車，我都說服左佢留低<br />\n之後佢係架車打左幾次警署電話，意料之內無人聽<br />\n之後都打過999，不過對方都係叫叔叔打番警署電話，真係打唔通都無辦法唯有等再夜啲繼續打<br />\n搞左一輪我叫叔叔都係同我去一去門口，最多我幫手拎個編號同警方了解左先，佢就行遠少少有需要先再叫佢<br />\n但佢最後話其實已經接觸過警方，警方叫佢聽日黎就ok (果陣街坊可能唔知，同埋又無警方證明可以遲一日報到嘅野，而大家都心急唔知會唔會因為遲左而對保釋有咩影響)<br />\n咁我問多幾次佢係咪真係接觸過，佢話係，佢驚警方話佢玩野黎完又黎，所以先咁抗拒我地陪佢入去<br />\n咁我見佢咁堅持就算了，臨走佢同我講左佢個故事<br />\n佢話佢都好憎警察，因為佢比警察屈襲警先要黎保釋報到<br />\n而且保釋金仲要成6位數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(佢比左張保釋紙我睇)<br />\n最後佢比左張佢公司嘅傳單我，我見佢咁慘就問佢介唔介意我將呢個故事放上網，睇下有冇人有生意可以搵佢幫下手，佢都ok左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叔叔係做驗窗的，如果深水埗嘅街坊有需要嘅記住搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他地區都可以打個電話問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7crar4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7crar4.png&h=778409cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NDFeTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NDFeTL.png&h=b6e8bdbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\np.s 打手死全家"},{"pid":"dedc75b4310ab1cb962cb4ad16aa17b63410c146","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c96d40bbf0cb0a377353f6d3f243f89367aa013","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c361e680fccadef2a2ac7b5f4577004684f2ff","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545a3df2fd324f057762703cf149b69d3eee4348","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6f12c655b6d842f99c1fa44b9fede9ca81bf65","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:46:53.000Z","msg":"玩完雷射槍再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bbaa086a226f1cc6f812966eee3113b39af1b7","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"街坊哥哥唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9932f56258624df6f47df8c27d62b8115d5b7a83","tid":1429192,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"試下推多日。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}